text: Prosopocera superbrunnea is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1969.BioLib.cz - Prosopocera superbrunnea. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1969
